    <title type="html"><![CDATA[How to Set Up a Multiple Author Blog]]></title>
    <link href="http://IPPETAD.github.io/blog/2014/04/09/how-to-set-up-a-multiple-author-blog/"/>
    <updated>2014-04-09T19:36:15-06:00</updated>
